.sprite {
    background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,);
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    display: block;
}

.sprite-close {
    width: 21px;
    height: 21px;
    background-position: -10px -10px;
}

    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background-position: -10px -51px;
}
